Dataset with world gdp and population in 2017 (or last reported values).

world_gdp_and_population_2017.Rd

tbd

data("world_gdp_and_population_2017")

Format

A data frame with 262 observations on the following 4 variables.

reporter_iso

a character vector

gdp_current_usd

a numeric vector

population_total

a numeric vector

gdp_pc_usd

a numeric vector

Source

The World Bank (obtained by using wbstats package)
